item.title: New grad vs senior dev [Eric Lipppert]
item.description: New grad vs senior dev. Eric Lipppert. Fabulous adventures in coding. https://ericlippert.com/2020/03/27/new-grad-vs-senior-dev/ . https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=22352674 . Mar 27, 2020. Substring Search in Visual Basic In CS, substring search is a foundational problem for which there are \(O(m + n)\) algorithms. But VB’s implementation was \(O(mn)\). Suppose we have InStr("apple banana orange", "banana"): Skip to the first b. Check if banana is a substring starting from that b.
